replies.bodyText:
I tried this locally, it seems to do the trick - be sure to test out both the client JAR and installer JAR:
configurations {
    datahubLogging
}

dependencies {
  ...
  datahubLogging 'ch.qos.logback:logback-classic:1.2.3'
}

// add this to both clientJar and bootJar
from(configurations.datahubLogging.collect { it.isDirectory() ? it : zipTree(it) }) {
        exclude "META-INF/*.SF"
        exclude "META-INF/*.DSA"
        exclude "META-INF/*.RSA"
    }
